The paper discusses the optimization of neural network classifiers, which falls under the category of machine learning. The use of gradient-based methods and loss functions also suggests a focus on deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other possible sub-categories include cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
